Thank you so much!
You are welcome!

This property was a true oasis - the perfect place to escape from the hustle and bustle of daily life. I loved the private pool and the serene surroundings.
I appreciated the little touches that the hosts added to the property, like the welcome basket of local goodies and the well-stocked kitchen. It made me feel right at home
